    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/773d5ab1423b3cb1126089c456556a0c.avif?t=1732003164\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br>《希望之光1灵菌涅槃》是一款充满挑战性的策略战棋游戏，玩家将作为一个冒险者，与各路能力突出鲜明的伙伴从相遇到一起并肩作战，一步步构建出最强冒险者小队！<br>精心设计的地图以及战术多变的敌人，让每一步行动都充满博弈，每一个敌人都需要全力以赴。对战场、阵型的把控将直接决定小队的生死！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事介绍</h2>本故事主要讲述了地球被外星种族奴役后，一群被选中的人们反抗压迫获得自由的故事。故事情节轻松诙谐，人物性格丰富多彩。除了游戏中的标准结局之外，游戏中还含有一个<strong>隐藏真结局</strong>等你来发掘。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/e87b6cf217de1965b9636e4da5bffe71.poster.avif?t=1732003164\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/e87b6cf217de1965b9636e4da5bffe71.webm?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/e87b6cf217de1965b9636e4da5bffe71.mp4?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2>与特色鲜明的有趣伙伴相遇，每个伙伴都有自己的<strong>专属技能</strong>，战斗方式也截然不同，利用好他们的能力，组建属于你的全能小队吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/53f7c923e47cbdde07479571e5eb3948.poster.avif?t=1732003164\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/53f7c923e47cbdde07479571e5eb3948.webm?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/53f7c923e47cbdde07479571e5eb3948.mp4?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>与高度智慧的敌人战斗，<strong>敌人的战术多种多样</strong>，全力集火造成减员、快速绕后偷袭牧师、侧方突袭俩面包抄等样样精通，每一次行动都是精彩的对弈交锋。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/69c9f77b43049966afc9198cd33f611c.poster.avif?t=1732003164\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/69c9f77b43049966afc9198cd33f611c.webm?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/69c9f77b43049966afc9198cd33f611c.mp4?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>精心设计的地图，进入树林、山谷、城堡、村庄等<strong>有利地形</strong>可以获得关键加成，为作战带来巨大优势。同时悬崖、狭窄通道等<strong>地形也会限制小队的站位</strong>，对战斗地形的选择将直接影响成败。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/be642ac5417f67f74634855d35d3689e.poster.avif?t=1732003164\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/be642ac5417f67f74634855d35d3689e.webm?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/be642ac5417f67f74634855d35d3689e.mp4?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>每个角色都有<strong>专属战斗动画</strong>和<strong>暴击特写动画</strong>，且会<strong>根据能力的不同拥有不同的战斗动画</strong>！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/2bbe8bc0ce7f195fc16a0c823f57bd82.poster.avif?t=1732003164\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/2bbe8bc0ce7f195fc16a0c823f57bd82.webm?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/2bbe8bc0ce7f195fc16a0c823f57bd82.mp4?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/7a6cdff38a6ac8ed518721cc8199f7c1.poster.avif?t=1732003164\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/7a6cdff38a6ac8ed518721cc8199f7c1.webm?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/7a6cdff38a6ac8ed518721cc8199f7c1.mp4?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/8f37b7531403bfb5cfebdc2f468158a1.poster.avif?t=1732003164\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/8f37b7531403bfb5cfebdc2f468158a1.webm?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/8f37b7531403bfb5cfebdc2f468158a1.mp4?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>特色<strong>缰绳坐骑系统</strong>，可通过使用缰绳来骑乘坐骑，以便来更改单位的移动方式！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/9612cc1498b9b41853933673e3b9edf2.poster.avif?t=1732003164\" width=326 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/9612cc1498b9b41853933673e3b9edf2.webm?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>对于希望挑战更高难度的硬核玩家，我们还准备了<strong>困难模式</strong>，队友一旦死亡将<strong>永久退场</strong>！",
